ithm is able to quickly verify its\noptimality. Furthermore, we demonstrate that our method is significantly faster\nthan the maximum flow based exact optimal algorithm. We conduct experiments on\ndatasets from broad domains, and our algorithm achieves $\\sim$145$\\times$\nspeedup on average to find subgraphs whose density is at least 90\\% of the\noptimal value.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Oct 2019 22:27:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Oct 2019 03:37:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-18"}
